Quincy.Eliot Congregational Church: Eliot Congregational Church ("Walnut Avenue Congregational Church" or "Eliot United Church of Christ") is an historic Congregational church at 56 Dale Street, at the corner of 118-120 Walnut Street in Boston, Massachusetts. The main church building was designed by J. Williams Beal and built in 1873. It is built out of Roxbury puddingstone.
